该论题具有实例”的论证效果。比如论证“在中国做实业仍然可以发家致富”时，你不用举什么董明珠，任正非，你举出什么王二狗，李三蛋做实业发家致富了，只要查有此事，那么论述就成立。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I1oOc5onDho4rEAMaCDI4ODUzOTMzIPG6t94FMAA49QFAGHIJMjk5NjAwMDY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"22 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-bc3dc54bab6a21f30566869a4d3f039e_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"25_1732798144.697163","card_id":"Q_4953432893","target":{"id":4953432893,"title":"为什么中国搞不出像\"阿贾克斯\"\"拉玛西亚\"这样类似的青训营？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4953432893","type":"question","created":1732375957,"answer_count":130,"follower_count":184,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1811,2955,32096,33803,45810],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"足球强不强大更看重的是传承，中国也有许多足球俱乐部，为什么搞不出像阿贾克斯、巴塞罗那拉玛西亚青训营一样的系统？？都有什么因素导致？？"},"attached_info":"CkEI1oOc5onDho4rEAMaCTExMTk2NzQwMCCV64e6BjAAOLgBQBlyCjQ5NTM0MzI4OTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"21 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d7990a865cac96e962f04f7c19da83cb_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"26_1732798144.701130","card_id":"Q_4786354832","target":{"id":4786354832,"title":"为什么现代职场越来越注重情商，而不单单看专业能力?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4786354832","type":"question","created":1732224238,"answer_count":247,"follower_count":450,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2566,4467],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEI1oOc5onDho4rEAMaCTExMTkzMzg4OCDuyf65BjAAOMIDQBpyCjQ3ODYzNTQ4MzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"21 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"